{"body": ["<tr><th>Project/Area Number</th><td>22890060</td></tr>", "<tr>\n     <th>Research Category</th>\n     <td>\n      \n    <p> \n        \n        \n      <a href=\"/search/?qc=Grant-in-Aid%20for%20Research%20Activity%20start-up\" class=\"link-page underline\">Grant-in-Aid for Research Activity start-up</a>\n    \n    </p>\n     </td></tr>", "<tr><th>Allocation Type</th><td>Single-year Grants</td></tr>", "<tr><th>Research Field</th>\n      <td>\n      \n      <a href=\"/search/?qd=Biological%20Sciences/Medicine%2C%20Dentistry%2C%20and%20Pharmacy/Basic%20medicine/Virology\" class=\"link-page underline\">Virology</a>\n      \n        </td></tr>", "<tr><th>Research Institution</th><td><a href=\"/search/?qe=Yamaguchi%20University\" class=\"link-page underline\">Yamaguchi University</a>(2011)<br><a href=\"/search/?qe=Tokyo%20University%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Technology\" class=\"link-page underline\">Tokyo University of Agriculture and Technology</a>(2010)</td></tr>", "<tr><th><h3><strong>Principal Investigator</strong></h3></th>\n          <td>\n          <h4><span><a href=\"/search/?qm=50435715\">WATANABE Rie</a></span>\u00a0\u00a0\u5c71\u53e3\u5927\u5b66,\u00a0\u8fb2\u5b66\u90e8,\u00a0\u51c6\u6559\u6388\u00a0(50435715)</h4>\n          </td></tr>", "<tr>\n     <th>Project Period (FY)</th>\n     <td>\n      <span class=\"fiscal_year\">2010\u00a0\u2013\u00a02011</span>\n     </td>\n    </tr>", "<tr>\n     <th>Project Status</th>\n     <td>\n      <span class=\"pstatus\">Completed(Fiscal Year 2011)</span>\n     </td>\n    </tr>", "<tr><th>Budget Amount\u00a0<a class=\"award_amount_help\" href=\"https://support.nii.ac.jp/kaken/project_details\" onclick=\"return winOpen(this.href);\">*help</a></th>\n    <td>\n     <h5>\u00a53,042,000 (Direct Cost : \u00a52,340,000\u3001Indirect Cost : \u00a5702,000)</h5>\n     \n     Fiscal Year 2011 : \u00a51,443,000 (Direct Cost : \u00a51,110,000\u3001Indirect Cost : \u00a5333,000)<br>\n     \n     Fiscal Year 2010 : \u00a51,599,000 (Direct Cost : \u00a51,230,000\u3001Indirect Cost : \u00a5369,000)\n     \n    </td></tr>", "<tr><th>Keywords</th><td>\u30a4\u30f3\u30d5\u30eb\u30a8\u30f3\u30b6\u30a6\u30a4\u30eb\u30b9 / \u30de\u30c8\u30ea\u30c3\u30af\u30b9\u30bf\u30f3\u30d1\u30af / \u591a\u91cf\u4f53\u5f62\u6210 / \u7c92\u5b50\u5185\u53d6\u8fbc\u307f / \u30a6\u30a4\u30eb\u30b9 / \u611f\u67d3\u75c7 / \u30bf\u30f3\u30d1\u30af\u8cea / \u30a4\u30f3\u30d5\u30eb\u30a8\u30f3\u30b6 / \u30de\u30c8\u30ea\u30c3\u30af\u30b9</td></tr>", "<tr>\n      <th>Research Abstract</th>\n      <td>\n        <p>We expressed Flag tagged M1(M1-FL) and HA tagged M1(HA-M1) together in HEK 293T cells and immunoprecipitated using anti-Flag antibody. In the precipitate, HA-M1 was detected in the westernblot analysis with anti-HA antibody. When M1 from filamentous virus A/ Udorn/ 72(H3N2) was analyzed in this system, it was shown that pH of the IP buffer did not affect the formation of complex. On the other hand, M1 from A/ WSN/ 33(H1N1), which forms spherical particle, formed the complex which showed susceptibility to the environmental pH.\n        \n        </p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>"]}
